Description of problem:
On an Lenovo T440p the scroll function of the touchpad don't work.

Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable):
xorg-x11-drv-libinput-0.10.0-5.fc22.x86_64

How reproducible:
Everytime

Steps to Reproduce:
1. dnf install xorg-x11-drv-libinput
2. reboot


Actual results:
The scoll area of the touchpad don't work.

Expected results:
Working touchpad with scroll function.

Additional info:
Removing the package will restore the scroll function.
two-finger scrolling or edge scrolling?

if the latter, see: https://bugs.freedesktop.org/show_bug.cgi?id=89381
Yes with edge scrolling.
deferring to upstream for now then, need to implement it there first
